text: Oleksiy Valeriyovych Honcharuk (; born July 7, 1984) is a Ukrainian politician and lawyer. Honcharuk was the 17th Prime Minister of Ukraine from 29 August 2019 to 4 March 2020. He was the Deputy Head of the Office of the President of Ukraine Zelensky. Honcharuk is the youngest Prime Minister in the modern Ukrainian history. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Ukraine Category:Ukrainian lawyers Category:People from Chernihiv Oblast
